Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamu, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. This is Hamu. As ordered,\NI brought those two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Drifters appear to be two old men,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are in the midst of a heated fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief! Thief! Why the hell\Nis this two-bit thief here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling "two-bit thief"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who should be called that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice lies with the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You stole it from me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You copied my strategy from Cannae\Nand used it in Zama, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, you old fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show me you can win, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grrr, why are you talking\Nlike a chosen one, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't steal it, since I won\Nthe war fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate the Romans!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I go back, I will salt all of Carthage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:01:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I go back, I will cross\Nthe Alps one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like me to do, Grand Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The issue is that their intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.30,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Octobrists"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find out what they are somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this world will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:01.32,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 2\NFootsteps"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, I've told you so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys went to that deserted\Ncastle again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've repeatedly told you not\Nto get involved with Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've warned you about entering the forest,\Ngoing to that deserted castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and associating with Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the lord and his men ever\Nfind out, they will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from them, got it?!\NAm I understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! It's before the harvest. Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've noticed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the smell of battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the "Elves."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be bandits or brigands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Elves are under attack. I smell the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are "Elves"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the strange folks\Nwho live beyond the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones with long ears who dragged you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! Are you going over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where I am or what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if this is a dream or reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the only thing left for me\Nis to charge forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the idiot, not me.\NHe was dying not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a human bullet or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they on the move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they going to do?\NWhat will happen to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow, too slow, Nobunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you,\NDemon King of the Sixth Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm already fifty, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you, Lord Toyohisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.34,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nineteen"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that smug smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This punk is completely different from the character in the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chronicle of the Genpei War.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He-Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your head with me! All right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Drifters in the deserted castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand you. I don't know\Nwhat the hell you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't speak Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have strange-looking ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two saved my life,\Ndidn't you? Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:13.03,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mutter mutter mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't speak Japanese, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell them to "die," too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Help!" Repeat after me. "Help!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it! "Help! Help!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help, help, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! That's that, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:37.47,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rumble rumble rumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to force the conclusion you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just witnessed fast-talking\Non par with that of the Ikko sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very well equipped.\NThey can't be brigands or bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regular soldiers? Are they the lord's forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These idiots. It's like they're\Nasking me to seize their land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's claim the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Claim"? Did he actually say, "claim"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of saying "take back,"\Nor "help them," he said, "claim," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's their nature,\Nand it's innate and pathological.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their most powerful ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's the only ability they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when or where they live,\Nthey have only one governing principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to conquer territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?\NWhat are you accusing us of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You entered the forest and\Nsaved a Drifter, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entering the forest, making bows,\Nand associating with Drifters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all serious crimes for Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save a dying man, the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children? Is that the reason\Nyou're asking me to overlook this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Elves are really disgraceful and insolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The administration of Drifters is a job for\Nmagicians of the Octobrist Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a serious crime for\Ndemihumans like you to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, you've been unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't be able to get firewood\Nor nuts without entering the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've forced us to work as serfs and\Nhave taken our women away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, these children save a\Ndying man and you call it a crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling us Elves to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You all should just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to curse at somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,put the blame on your ancestors who lost the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, Elves, Dwarves, Hobbits,\Nand all demihuman races will be extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just culling your population.\NHow many shall I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told I'm allowed to\Neliminate up to 50% of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my life instead. Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're still young.\NYou have to take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a future... as a pathetic serf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for your brothers who saved\Nthe Drifter, they're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They started this whole mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably corpses by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll become feed for\Nthe insects of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a fire in the wheat filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's before the harvest time!\NI'll lose the tax money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been telling you to keep\Nan eye on it, haven't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set fire to their field?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Those without dignity can\Nsurvive if they have food to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those without food can endure their\Nhunger as long as they have dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those who have lost both stop caring\Nand desperately cling to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the tactic the Ikko sect\Nkept employing against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best way to steal a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a frightening person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire still looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of Ise Nagashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our field...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Put out the fire! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible. It has spread too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr... if... ter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a commander's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the commander, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, leave your head here!\NThat's the head of the commander, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a Drifter.\NWhat the hell is he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... a Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masha! Mark! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scary-looking man saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are Drifters?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drifter, are you interfering with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your head.\NJust leave your life here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what on earth\Nyou are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, a barbarian who can't even speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk with swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aram is not an ordinary soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a real knight backed by the magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a Drifter can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kumite style anti-armor technique\Nwith the sheath of a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies who were fleeing are no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is scary, but so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what is he going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, kill him. Kill him.\NYou must put an end to his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where we are or who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the revenge you must take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid is telling you to avenge him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't understand his words,\Nbut they know what he's been telling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is quite something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You damn Elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the consequences...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong... S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell were you?\NYou know I'm still recuperating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've been busy with other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.13,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rumble rumble rumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, you must be tired.\NPlease take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to sit down,\Nbut I'll let you take my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.60,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gleam"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my gosh! Oh, my gosh! I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Master, those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.75,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shimazu Toyohisa Seizes\NControl of Elf Village?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still wasting your time\Nstruggling, huh, Murasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you try,\Nno matter how many Drifters you send,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much effort\Nyou make, it's all futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, Easy.\NThe wrongs must be righted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, Easy. I won't let you have your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the pathetic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can do it, go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.60,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black King Commences Southern Invasion"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:21:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way your Drifters\Ncould possibly beat my Ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Semu, this is Semu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Master, they finally seized the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to let them run loose!\NI'll bring them there immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't work. There's no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring them here. Don't you come, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
